elements.name: Add a user and validate the user has been added to the table

steps.name: User is on the practice page
User clicks on Add User button
new window pops up and user has to input information
User has to fill out First Name field
User has to fill out Last Name field
User has to fill out User Name field
User has to fill out Password field
User has to chose a role
User needs to add phone number and click Save button
User should be able to see his info added to the list

elements.name: Delete the user "novak" from the table and validate the user has been deleted.

steps.name: User locates novak user and clicks on remove icon
new window pops up and User needs to click ok button
User can confirm that novak information has been deleted successfully
